room_title: Escape room "Thor" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: Had a blast with my family and friends and cant wait to do another room!! It was challenging but still exciting. Loved the experience and staff was kind and helpful too

room_title: Escape room "Thor" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: Good experience. Everyone had fun and the group enjoyed working as a team. Hopefully will do again next year for my birthday.

room_title: Escape room "Thor" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: Enjoyed the challenges and the creativity that went into these rooms. I like the process of what it takes to get hints when needed and our moderator was very energetic. He was also very cute. Just to put that out there.
